# DO NOT

- DO NOT use `var`
- DO NOT put game logic in Scene files — use managers
- DO NOT use magic numbers — use constants.js
- DO NOT access another scene's properties directly — use this.game.events
- DO NOT hardcode canvas dimensions — use this.scale.width / this.scale.height
- DO NOT load external image assets — generate all textures procedurally in BootScene
- DO NOT call sprite.destroy() on pooled objects — use setActive(false) instead
- DO NOT use setInterval/setTimeout — use this.time.addEvent()
- DO NOT edit PROGRESS.md
